{"tid":2305140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國抗議者高舉黃鴨包圍軍營 鼓勵部隊發動政變","createTime":"2020-11-29T11:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T14:42:44.000Z","uid":337052,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"698aae8f46f3b7a0b7fdb50f310051613aec2ec8","tid":2305140,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">集會組織於第11步兵團前發起集會！</span></strong><br />\n2020年11月29日 - by hushjoker<br />\nSHARETWEETSHARE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%9A-6-5-696x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E0%25B8%25A1%25E0%25B9%2587%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%259A-6-5-696x400.jpg&h=a48a7680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊 據泰媒報導 11月29日，<span class=\"red\">集會組織&ldquo;法政與示威陣線&rdquo;聯盟於當地時間15時在皇家衛隊第11步兵團前發起集會。</span>據悉，此前集會組織原定於第1步兵團前發起集會，但從29日凌晨起，工作人員陸續運來100多個集裝箱以及鐵絲圈等屏障物將第1步兵團前的道路和路口封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/S__188334097-696x523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FS__188334097-696x523.jpg&h=3e544f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/S__188334101-696x523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FS__188334101-696x523.jpg&h=e32114e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B9%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%82%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E0%25B8%2595%25E0%25B8%25B9%25E0%25B9%2589%25E0%25B8%2584%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%2599%25E0%25B9%2580%25E0%25B8%2597%25E0%25B8%2599%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%2599%25E0%25B9%2580%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%25A3%25E0%25B9%258C%25E0%25B8%2582%25E0%25B8%25A7%25E0%25B8%25B2%25E0%25B8%2587.jpg&h=efad942d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/S__12304415-1441x1080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FS__12304415-1441x1080.jpg&h=d1cbd3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/S__12304422-1441x1080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FS__12304422-1441x1080.jpg&h=93b35f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/S__12304404-1-1441x1080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FS__12304404-1-1441x1080.jpg&h=131d7906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11月29日上午10時，集會組織宣布將集會地點變更至第11步兵團前方。隨後陸續有警方、空軍等進入集會現場以維護秩序，並有工作人員運來鐵絲圈、廢舊的公交車、樹樁等做屏障。 13時40分左右，已有兩輛水砲車至現場待命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%9A-3-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E0%25B8%25A1%25E0%25B9%2587%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%259A-3-10.jpg&h=3429dd22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%9A-4-8-696x392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E0%25B8%25A1%25E0%25B9%2587%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%259A-4-8-696x392.jpg&h=a44ef505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%9A-6-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E0%25B8%25A1%25E0%25B9%2587%25E0%25B8%25AD%25E0%25B8%259A-6-5.jpg&h=5d2de2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20201026165134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587_20201026165134.jpg&h=dbfa64db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14時50分左右，集會組織頭領之一的&ldquo;企鵝&rdquo;來到集會現場附近，<span class=\"red\">並表示今日之所以選擇在第1步兵團和第11步兵團前集會，是因為兩隻機構與此前的政變有著很重要的關聯。</span> （編譯：hush 來源：Khaosod）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/S__47595525-696x522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FS__47595525-696x522.jpg&h=1e63fc7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%e4%ba%8e%e7%ac%ac11%e6%ad%a5%e5%85%b5%e5%9b%a2%e5%89%8d%e5%8f%91%e8%b5%b7%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%ef%bc%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2F%25e9%259b%2586%25e4%25bc%259a%25e7%25bb%2584%25e7%25bb%2587%25e4%25ba%258e%25e7%25ac%25ac11%25e6%25ad%25a5%25e5%2585%25b5%25e5%259b%25a2%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%258f%2591%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e9%259b%2586%25e4%25bc%259a%25ef%25bc%2581%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=480caef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%e4%ba%8e%e7%ac%ac11%e6%ad%a5%e5%85%b5%e5%9b%a2%e5%89%8d%e5%8f%91%e8%b5%b7%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%ef%bc%81/</a>"},{"pid":"0f51257d201d7e7abf3bb1b26b4d36990ca416f3","tid":2305140,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"